  <brief_title>Safety and Pharmacokinetic Study of EMBEDA in Children Ages 7-17 With Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label Study To Evaluate The Safety And Pharmacokinetics Of Pf-06412528 In Children 7-17 Years For The Treatment Of Moderate-to-severe Pain</official_title>
  <sponsors>
